          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-9120 lnet: override global message timeout",
        "message": "LU-9120 lnet: override global message timeout\n\nAdded a parameter to LNetGet() and LNetPut() which overrides\nthe global message timeout if it is set to non-zero.\nThe caller of the LNetGet() and LNetPut() can dictate how long\nto wait for a REPLY/ACK before a timeout event is generated\nby LNet.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I370f54d36a796505ed86ad1d37c66a080ac2c056\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/multi-rail"
    }
  },
